.DT
calc_change
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
calc_change

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
calc_change -  This method calculates the change of a certain value from a given money array.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mixed calc_change(int value,
mixed * mon_array)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^value%^RESET%^ - the value of the change to calculate
%^BOLD%^mon_array%^RESET%^ - the money array to determine the change from
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the money array containing the change to use
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/money_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method calculates the change of a certain value from a
given money array.   This makes sure that the change does not include
money that does not actually exist.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
make_payment(), pay_amount_from()

.EP

